column3: Please don't make direct changes to the leveldb directory. If you want to convert their README to md, submit a patch upstream.\n

Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/d3081fa2314ac064c1054b58f4b11c332af6fe09 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu
